                        <p>The city’s decision represents an unfortunate loss for the people of London, and for freedom more broadly as a guiding societal ideal.</p>
<p><em>Ian Buchanan is a Trinity sophomore. His column, "let freedom ring," runs on alternate Wednesdays.</em></p>

